00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,433
不要管其它人
Don't ever let anybody

2
00:00:01,501 --> 00:00:03,935
说他们比你强 福雷斯
tell you they're better than you, Forrest.

3
00:00:04,005 --> 00:00:06,439
如果上帝要让人人都一样的话
If God intended everybody to be the same,

4
00:00:06,508 --> 00:00:09,443
他会给每人一双脚撑
he'd have given us all braces on our legs.

5
00:00:09,511 --> 00:00:13,447
妈妈总有办法让我明白她的意思
Mama always had a way of explaining things so I could understand them.

6
00:00:13,650 --> 00:00:17,985
我们住在17号公路附近
We lived about a quarter mile off Route 17,

7
00:00:18,055 --> 00:00:20,990
距离亚拉巴马州绿茵镇约半哩
about a half mile from the town of Greenbow, Alabama.

8
00:00:21,059 --> 00:00:23,994
这个地方属于绿茵县
That's in the county of Greenbow.

9
00:00:24,063 --> 00:00:26,497
我们的房子来自妈妈的家族
Our house had been in Mama's family

10
00:00:26,566 --> 00:00:28,625
从她爷爷的爷爷的爷爷传下来的
since her grandpa's grandpa's grandpa

11
00:00:28,702 --> 00:00:32,138
他大概在一千年前飘洋过海来这里
had come across the ocean about a thousand years ago.

12
00:00:32,207 --> 00:00:34,573
房子只有我和妈妈住
Since it was just me and Mama

13
