mostly to people passing through,

16
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:44,245
比如从莫比镇、或蒙哥马利镇来的人
Like from, oh, Mobile, Montgomery, places like that.

17
00:00:44,322 --> 00:00:47,257
我和妈妈靠这个挣到钱
That's how me and Mama got money.

18
00:00:47,325 --> 00:00:50,089
妈妈是个很聪明的女士
Mama was a real smart lady.

19
00:00:50,162 --> 00:00:52,096
记住我说的话,福雷斯
Remember what I told you, Forrest.

